ily: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><ul style="list-style-type: none;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;">项目推广：</strong></p></li></ul><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">总体定位&nbsp;-------&nbsp;品质派旅游地产商</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">Slogan：江南液上海，休闲水乡情</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>', N'', N'来自火星的程序猿', N'/106/109\148.html', N'', N'0', N'1')
